	Kom installation


*** What you need ***
- OCaml 3.09.0 or above installed
- LablGtk 2.6.0 or above installed (with lablglade enabled)
- XML-light 2 or above installed
- Cameleon 1.9.13 or above installed (including native code libraries)
- OCaml-MySQL 1.0.3 or above installed
- make ;-)

*** How to compile ***
- ./configure [--prefix=/path/to/install]
  By default, install all in /usr/local/bin
- make depend
- make all [or only 'make byte' if the native code compiler is not installed]
- make install
  The list of installed or not installed files is printed.
